author: WillFroom
message:
[XLA:CPU/GPU] Move symbolic_tile to shared directory.

PiperOrigin-RevId: 814146527

files.patch:
@@ -185,3 +185,37 @@ cc_library(
         "@llvm-project//mlir:Support",
     ],
 )
+
+cc_library(
+    name = "symbolic_tile",
+    srcs = ["symbolic_tile.cc"],
+    hdrs = ["symbolic_tile.h"],
+    deps = [
+        ":affine_map_evaluator",
+        ":constraint_expression",
+        ":size_and_stride_expression",
+        "//xla/hlo/analysis:indexing_analysis",
+        "@com_google_absl//absl/algorithm:container",
+        "@com_google_absl//absl/log",
+        "@com_google_absl//absl/log:check",
+        "@com_google_absl//absl/types:span",
+        "@llvm-project//llvm:Support",
+        "@llvm-project//mlir:IR",
+        "@llvm-project//mlir:Support",
+    ],
+)
+
+xla_cc_test(
+    name = "symbolic_tile_test",
+    srcs = ["symbolic_tile_test.cc"],
+    deps = [
+        ":affine_map_evaluator",
+        ":symbolic_tile",
+        "//xla/hlo/analysis:indexing_analysis",
+        "//xla/hlo/analysis:indexing_test_utils",
+        "//xla/tests:xla_internal_test_main",
+        "@com_google_absl//absl/strings:string_view",
+        "@com_google_absl//absl/types:span",
+        "@com_google_googletest//:gtest",
+    ],
+)
